dth=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/2j5X6pZ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/UJXJ5gQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/DXcKlJf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/vTsTyrz.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/mQgIVDu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/5xXqhXe.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/kVHzJV9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/juC5EIY.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/cYHSkb2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/YZOb4UU.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/G8igFBt.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/GuGTe3L.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/FaXxWL6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/UfXH7G1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/WIrXyN1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/6OH4xcy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/OY7leD2.png\" width=\"222\" height=\"40\" /><br /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/UWFTH8U.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/xihe1Iq.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/mttOKJb.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8U6EqW7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/EY1Banv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/pRShE0c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/xyN0hmi.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/rTI2Gj5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/AZV6lTm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/Yc3s8na.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/iqjbhOr.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/sy21BTe.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/4uSaqGJ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/AEX6ikk.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/hK2Ne4q.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/OofG9DM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/u6uA7Yo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/wm2UCet.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/Cw074li.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/2j5X6pZ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/DXcKlJf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/vTsTyrz.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/mQgIVDu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/5xXqhXe.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/kVHzJV9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/cYHSkb2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/GuGTe3L.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/pcmP0xG.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/5EiwS3H.png\" width=\"253\" height=\"40\" /><br /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/UWFTH8U.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/xihe1Iq.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/mttOKJb.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/1S9UjyX.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8U6EqW7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/EY1Banv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/pRShE0c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/ajOKaqG.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/xyN0hmi.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/1h9o2Kx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Merge Enchantments is a mod where you can mix and exclude the enchantments even combine everything. some examples are&nbsp;Sharpness, Smite and Bane of arthropods, All types of Protection (Fire, Blast and Projectile, Silk Touch and Fortune, Riptide with Channeling/Loyalty, Density, Breach, Smite and Bane of Arthropods. Check the <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Merge-Enchantments/wiki\">Wiki</a> and find how works the config where you can make a <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Merge-Enchantments/wiki/Config#blacklist\">blacklist</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Merge-Enchantments/wiki/Config#blacklist\">combine everything</a>.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/H9nhuOr.gif\" width=\"414\" height=\"233\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://imgur.com/l717aDK.gif\" width=\"414\" height=\"234\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/1h9o2Kx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>F.A.Q.s</strong></span></em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: Does it work with other mods enchantments?</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A: Since the version 3.0 it's possible to merge all vanilla and external mod enchantments</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: How can i get <span style=\"color: #008000;\">Silk touch</span> and <span style=\"color: #99cc00;\">Fortune</span> together?</strong><br />A: You have to install Merge Enchantments and <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/toggle-enchantments\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Toggle Enchantments<br /></a><strong>Q: How can i get <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">Riptide</span> with <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Loyalty</span> and <span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Channeling</span>?</strong><br />A: You have to install Merge Enchantments and <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/improved-trident-enchantments\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Improved Trident Enchantments</a></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: Can i include Merge Enchantments in my mod pack?</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A: Sure, just put my mod in the related projects</span></li>\n</ul>",
